  <brief_title>Low Cost Interventions to Improve Adherence to Childhood Immunization Schedule</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized Controlled Trial of Low Cost Interventions to Improve Adherence to Childhood Immunization Schedule in a Low Literacy Population in Pakistan</official_title>
  <sponsors>
