  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of the study was to assess the effect of 1) redesigned immunization card, 2)
      center-based education to mothers, and 3) redesigned card with center-based education to
      mothers, provided at DPT1, on DPT3 completion in a randomized controlled trial at rural
      Expanded Programme on Immunization (EPI) centers in Karachi, Pakistan.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
